commit.message: Added page that lists detailed platform error messages. Also added quick mailing list view, to show who has signed up.
Updates to platform to log detailed errors in db.
Updated repo model to include errors to allow us to easily trace down problems. Also includes slight reorg of execution info meta data
Fixed null pointer bug in invite dates
Updated admin invite page with dates.
Added dates to invitation requests for tracking. Ensured tokens can only be used once.
Ensured ownership of projects on import.
Added owns and starred stats boxes to profile and admin.
Added page view stats and plot to admin section.
Removed some sysouts
Added the ability to star project. Starred projects are listed on the user's dashboard. Project page shows how many stars it has.
Added a bit more info on the user profile page - starred projects and owned projects.
Merged
Fixed bug in web app importer page. Required small changes in sf and gh importer - to use the new unique project ID generator
Updated the add project page. Now allows multiple technology types; assigns the project to the creator.
Implemented better search for the website.
Ensured querystring params are passed to api.
Padded zeros to date strings
Updated to latest version of metvis - fixes axis display issue
Updates to various proeprties files.
Fixed consist JSON parsing.
Fixed inconsistent JSON responses
Closed mongo connections
Updated all MP plugins build properies to ensure vis folder is included in binary build
feature.xml includes Jetty plugins. product updated to auto start jetty plugins - required in order to ensure restlet starts a jetty server, rather than the default
Admin API now uses latest version of restlet
API: / now returns valid JSON. Updated Api to use latest version of restlet.
Fix for schedulers not updating that they've completed work.
Issue #7. I have set a GitHubBugTracker's url field to default https://api.github.com/repos/<projectId>/issues.

More features for the Admin API. Can get Platform status, project counts (inc those in error), and summary of the cluster.
Added gratuitous CSS animation to navigation menu.
Added node identifiers to the configuration file. Slaves identify themselves with these. Allows multiple slaves to run on the same machines.
Implemented utility Admin API resources. Allows easier monitoring of a running system.
